article_id:1349,category_name:News,title_name:Announcing Gala Dragalia!,image_path:,message:<div>Gala Dragalia will start at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1590732000"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>What is Gala Dragalia?</div><div>・The initial appearance rate for 5★ adventurers and dragons will be boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%! If you get a 5★ summon or 5★ featured summon, the appearance rate will return to the initial 6%.</div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Note: The newly added 5★ adventurers Radiant Xuan Zang (light) and Zhu Bajie (light), 4★ adventurer Sha Wujing (light), and 5★ dragon Tie Shan Gongzhu (light) will also appear in the next summon showcase.</span></div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia event duration:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1590732000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1591163940"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at some of the newly featured adventurers and dragons below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurers:</div><div>
